# microservice — minimal .d2 auto-layout path: person → services → database.
user:   User { shape: person }
api:    API Gateway
queue:  Job Queue { shape: queue }
worker: Worker
db:     Database { shape: cylinder }
cache:  Cache    { shape: cylinder }

user   -> api:   request
api    -> queue: enqueue
api    -> cache: lookup
queue  -> worker
worker -> db:    write
worker -> cache: update
